:::Bluestreak:::

OOC: My first attempt on a female character so bear with me

::He speeds ahead of Striker and Spears, and sits down in front of the ark.  
He was feeling really lonely recently and seeing how in love Striker and 
Spears were he had this great need for someone of his own.  After a while a 
stasis pod crashed down.  A golden eagle emerged from it::
Andromeda: Andromeda, Maximize!
::The Golden eagle transformed into a VERY beutiful looking fembot.  The 
walked up to the ark gates and said to Bluestreak::
Andromeda: Hey there, can i join your group?
::Bluestreak looked dumbfounded.  Her beauty was like an assault::
Bluestreak: Um, um, yeah.
::Andromeda smiled::
Andromeda: Lead the way.
::Bluestreak stumbled as he walked.  Maybe things were looking up for him...::
